1
00:00:03,960 --> 00:00:05,669
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

2
00:00:09,589 --> 00:00:11,485
<Default><b>I don't think
he's following us.</b></Default>

3
00:00:11,509 --> 00:00:13,429
<Default><b>Motoyasu, you asshole.</b></Default>

4
00:00:14,599 --> 00:00:16,679
<Default><b>[FILO]
But what about my carriage?</b></Default>

5
00:00:17,890 --> 00:00:19,390
<Default><b>[Motoyasu panting]</b></Default>

6
00:00:20,149 --> 00:00:21,666
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
We give up on it for now.</b></Default>

7
00:00:21,690 --> 00:00:24,130
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Motoyasu
might be staking it out.</b></Default>

8
00:00:26,859 --> 00:00:27,939
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

9
00:00:28,149 --> 00:00:30,660
<Default><b>Filo, come back!</b></Default>

10
00:00:31,489 --> 00:00:33,765
<Default><b>We'll get your carriage back
when it's safe.</b></Default>

11
00:00:33,789 --> 00:00:35,450
<Default><b>Okay, Master.</b></Default>

12
00:00:36,119 --> 00:00:38,670
<Default><b>- Master Naofumi look.
- Huh?</b></Default>

13
00:00:39,710 --> 00:00:41,270
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Filo, stop.</b></Default>

14
00:00:44,130 --> 00:00:45,920
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

15
00:00:49,630 --> 00:00:50,630
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

16
00:00:50,679 --> 00:00:52,390
<Default><b>You're the Shield Hero</b></Default>

17
00:00:52,719 --> 00:00:54,239
<Default><b>Yeah, that's right.</b></Default>

18
00:00:56,560 --> 00:00:58,060
<Default><b>I see.</b></Default>

19
00:01:00,479 --> 00:01:01,770
<Default><b>You're mine!</b></Default>

20
00:01:01,899 --> 00:01:03,310
<Default><b>Die!</b></Default>

21
00:01:04,980 --> 00:01:06,439
<Default><b>Meteor Shield!</b></Default>

22
00:01:06,530 --> 00:01:07,665
<Default><b>[thudding]</b></Default>

23
00:01:07,689 --> 00:01:08,926
<Default><b>You're wide open!</b></Default>

24
00:01:08,950 --> 00:01:10,280
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

25
00:01:11,200 --> 00:01:13,215
<Default><b>Who are you?
And what do you want?</b></Default>

26
00:01:13,239 --> 00:01:14,599
<Default><b>[both grunting]</b></Default>

27
00:01:14,950 --> 00:01:15,950
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

28
00:01:16,909 --> 00:01:18,426
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Raphtalia! Filo!</b></Default>

29
00:01:18,450 --> 00:01:20,000
<Default><b>Zweit Aura!</b></Default>

30
00:01:20,750 --> 00:01:22,040
<Default><b>[evil laugh]</b></Default>

31
00:01:22,829 --> 00:01:24,896
<Default><b>It looks like the rumors
are actually true!</b></Default>

32
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:27,840
<Default><b>The Cardinal Weapon Heroes
really do love their harems!</b></Default>

33
00:01:28,209 --> 00:01:31,090
<Default><b>You're finished!
Summon Meteor Strike!</b></Default>

34
00:01:32,340 --> 00:01:33,849
<Default><b>[thunders]</b></Default>

35
00:01:34,510 --> 00:01:35,719
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

36
00:01:52,239 --> 00:01:53,359
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

37
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:28,379
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

38
00:03:31,210 --> 00:03:34,419
<Default><b>Five seconds until you're dead.
Good luck.</b></Default>

39
00:03:34,629 --> 00:03:35,759
<Default><b>Five.</b></Default>

40
00:03:36,590 --> 00:03:39,009
<Default><b>Air Strike Shield!
Second Shield!</b></Default>

41
00:03:39,099 --> 00:03:40,419
<Default><b>Dritte Shield!</b></Default>

42
00:03:40,969 --> 00:03:41,985
<Default><b>[MAN 05-A] Four.</b></Default>

43
00:03:42,009 --> 00:03:43,906
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Zweit Aura activate!</b></Default>

44
00:03:43,930 --> 00:03:45,115
<Default><b>[MAN 05-A] Three!</b></Default>

45
00:03:45,139 --> 00:03:46,899
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Raphtalia! Filo!</b></Default>

46
00:03:47,439 --> 00:03:48,839
<Default><b>- Right!
- Right!</b></Default>

47
00:03:48,900 --> 00:03:50,400
<Default><b>Two!</b></Default>

48
00:03:50,689 --> 00:03:52,110
<Default><b>[screams]</b></Default>

49
00:03:52,270 --> 00:03:54,360
<Default><b>Dispelling
Bullet: Doton!</b></Default>

50
00:03:54,439 --> 00:03:55,610
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

51
00:03:56,150 --> 00:03:57,490
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

52
00:03:59,120 --> 00:04:00,635
<Default><b>What just happened?</b></Default>

53
00:04:00,659 --> 00:04:01,899
<Default><b>[evil laugh]</b></Default>

54
00:04:01,949 --> 00:04:04,000
<Default><b>I dispelled
your buff magic.</b></Default>

55
00:04:04,199 --> 00:04:05,580
<Default><b>One!</b></Default>

56
00:04:07,169 --> 00:04:08,330
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

57
00:04:08,580 --> 00:04:10,580
<Default><b>What? He blocked that?</b></Default>

58
00:04:13,460 --> 00:04:14,710
<Default><b>Zero!</b></Default>

59
00:04:17,009 --> 00:04:18,470
<Default><b>Shield Prison!</b></Default>

60
00:04:18,550 --> 00:04:19,870
<Default><b>Meteor Shield!</b></Default>

61
00:04:22,550 --> 00:04:24,060
<Default><b>[blasting]</b></Default>

62
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:27,680
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

63
00:04:28,810 --> 00:04:30,560
<Default><b>[blasting]</b></Default>

64
00:04:32,060 --> 00:04:34,399
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

65
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:46,699
<Default><b>[blasts]</b></Default>

66
00:04:56,709 --> 00:04:58,800
<Default><b>[evil laugh]</b></Default>

67
00:05:00,379 --> 00:05:02,339
<Default><b>So you're still
alive, are ya?</b></Default>

68
00:05:03,220 --> 00:05:06,060
<Default><b>Oh, well, I'll just
have to finish you off!</b></Default>

69
00:05:15,689 --> 00:05:17,110
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

70
00:05:22,029 --> 00:05:23,529
<Default><b>I'll handle this.</b></Default>

71
00:05:25,370 --> 00:05:27,210
<Default><b>[MAN 05-A]
Well, well, well.</b></Default>

72
00:05:27,410 --> 00:05:29,386
<Default><b>If it isn't the
Vassal Weapon Wielder</b></Default>

73
00:05:29,410 --> 00:05:30,935
<Default><b>from a destroyed world.</b></Default>

74
00:05:30,959 --> 00:05:32,396
<Default><b>And here I thought
you were dead.</b></Default>

75
00:05:32,420 --> 00:05:34,500
<Default><b>- [evil laugh]
- I'm curious.</b></Default>

76
00:05:34,579 --> 00:05:37,339
<Default><b>Why bother saving the
Cardinal Heroes of this world</b></Default>

77
00:05:37,379 --> 00:05:40,339
<Default><b>when they're not even capable
of defending themselves?</b></Default>

78
00:05:40,839 --> 00:05:42,276
<Default><b>Honestly, I'm
disappointed</b></Default>

79
00:05:42,300 --> 00:05:44,365
<Default><b>they're a lot weaker
than expected.</b></Default>

80
00:05:44,389 --> 00:05:46,989
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA] We're weak?
Is that what you think?</b></Default>

81
00:05:53,060 --> 00:05:55,286
<Default><b>[MAn 05-B] Why
did she suddenly get faster!</b></Default>

82
00:05:55,310 --> 00:05:58,390
<Default><b>You dispelled the enchantment
Master Naofumi had put on me.</b></Default>

83
00:05:58,990 --> 00:06:00,375
<Default><b>Meaning you
dispelled the curse</b></Default>

84
00:06:00,399 --> 00:06:02,559
<Default><b>that had been
afflicting me as well!</b></Default>

85
00:06:06,490 --> 00:06:07,660
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

86
00:06:14,290 --> 00:06:15,829
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

87
00:06:15,920 --> 00:06:18,209
<Default><b>I-I have to
retreat before I...</b></Default>

88
00:06:18,300 --> 00:06:19,550
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

89
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:29,680
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

90
00:06:35,769 --> 00:06:37,529
<Default><b>That's not
the end of it.</b></Default>

91
00:06:37,980 --> 00:06:40,060
<Default><b>They will return
again eventually.</b></Default>

92
00:06:40,279 --> 00:06:42,610
<Default><b>That was
convenient timing</b></Default>

93
00:06:44,069 --> 00:06:46,319
<Default><b>Indeed, are you okay?</b></Default>

94
00:06:46,410 --> 00:06:48,425
<Default><b>You showed up
right after they attacked.</b></Default>

95
00:06:48,449 --> 00:06:50,016
<Default><b>Hate to point fingers.</b></Default>

96
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:52,440
<Default><b>But you're not working
with them, are you?</b></Default>

97
00:06:52,620 --> 00:06:54,000
<Default><b>Master Naofumi</b></Default>

98
00:06:54,079 --> 00:06:56,146
<Default><b>don't you think
that's going too far?</b></Default>

99
00:06:56,170 --> 00:06:58,170
<Default><b>She did save
us after all.</b></Default>

100
00:06:58,750 --> 00:07:01,379
<Default><b>- Even so.
- [stomach growling]</b></Default>

101
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:07,470
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

102
00:07:16,689 --> 00:07:18,360
<Default><b>[all gasp]</b></Default>

103
00:07:24,860 --> 00:07:25,966
<Default><b>Just so we're clear</b></Default>

104
00:07:25,990 --> 00:07:28,045
<Default><b>I still don't trust
this girl yet.</b></Default>

105
00:07:28,069 --> 00:07:29,545
<Default><b>But she seemed so hungry</b></Default>

106
00:07:29,569 --> 00:07:31,596
<Default><b>and we couldn't leave
her out there to starve.</b></Default>

107
00:07:31,620 --> 00:07:33,699
<Default><b>[FILO] I'm hungry</b></Default>

108
00:07:34,540 --> 00:07:37,000
<Default><b>Now, who are
you? Don't lie.</b></Default>

109
00:07:39,089 --> 00:07:40,729
<Default><b>My name is S'yne Lokk.</b></Default>

110
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:43,050
<Default><b>So why'd you save us
back there?</b></Default>

111
00:07:43,420 --> 00:07:45,879
<Default><b>Those men</b></Default>

112
00:07:45,970 --> 00:07:48,259
<Default><b>back in my world
and helped destroy it.</b></Default>

113
00:07:48,339 --> 00:07:50,076
<Default><b>Wait, destroyed
your world?</b></Default>

114
00:07:50,100 --> 00:07:51,930
<Default><b>Then that means</b></Default>

115
00:07:52,009 --> 00:07:53,536
<Default><b>that we went to before</b></Default>

116
00:07:53,560 --> 00:07:55,206
<Default><b>there could be
many others out there.</b></Default>

117
00:07:55,230 --> 00:07:56,689
<Default><b>Yeah, I guess so.</b></Default>

118
00:07:57,060 --> 00:07:58,780
<Default><b>I suppose it checks out.</b></Default>

119
00:07:58,850 --> 00:08:00,836
<Default><b>They did call you
the Vassal Weapon Wielder</b></Default>

120
00:08:00,860 --> 00:08:02,900
<Default><b>from a destroyed world
after all.</b></Default>

121
00:08:03,819 --> 00:08:05,689
<Default><b>Unfortunately,
it's true.</b></Default>

122
00:08:05,990 --> 00:08:08,005
<Default><b>The heroes in my world
were killed.</b></Default>

123
00:08:08,029 --> 00:08:10,109
<Default><b>And the world
destroyed with them.</b></Default>

124
00:08:10,569 --> 00:08:11,949
<Default><b>I understand.</b></Default>

125
00:08:12,699 --> 00:08:13,829
<Default><b>Now then.</b></Default>

126
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:15,175
<Default><b>Why don't you tell me</b></Default>

127
00:08:15,199 --> 00:08:18,159
<Default><b>how you were able to show up
at just the perfect moment?</b></Default>

128
00:08:24,209 --> 00:08:25,300
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

129
00:08:27,170 --> 00:08:28,680
<Default><b>With this...</b></Default>

130
00:08:29,589 --> 00:08:30,930
<Default><b>I tracked you.</b></Default>

131
00:08:31,720 --> 00:08:33,320
<Default><b>And watched over you.</b></Default>

132
00:08:34,429 --> 00:08:35,905
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Is that...</b></Default>

133
00:08:35,929 --> 00:08:38,190
<Default><b>Something akin
to a portal skill?</b></Default>

134
00:08:38,389 --> 00:08:39,909
<Default><b>When'd you do that?</b></Default>

135
00:08:39,980 --> 00:08:41,360
<Default><b>The coliseum.</b></Default>

136
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:43,149
<Default><b>During our fight?</b></Default>

137
00:08:43,230 --> 00:08:46,649
<Default><b>Wait, so you've been
watching me since then?</b></Default>

138
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:51,159
<Default><b>I don't want to see any more
Weapon Wielders killed.</b></Default>

139
00:08:51,820 --> 00:08:53,659
<Default><b>Once is more
than enough.</b></Default>

140
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:57,330
<Default><b>I'll help...
only if you let me.</b></Default>

141
00:09:00,919 --> 00:09:02,539
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

142
00:09:17,389 --> 00:09:19,456
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] She told us that
her world was destroyed</b></Default>

143
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:21,640
<Default><b>alongside
the Weapon Wielders in it.</b></Default>

144
00:09:22,690 --> 00:09:24,245
<Default><b>Which means
there are other worlds</b></Default>

145
00:09:24,269 --> 00:09:25,629
<Default><b>like I thought.</b></Default>

146
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:29,000
<Default><b>I'm curious about
what those two assailants said</b></Default>

147
00:09:29,240 --> 00:09:31,176
<Default><b>about her being
a Vassal Weapon Wielder</b></Default>

148
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:32,880
<Default><b>from a destroyed world.</b></Default>

149
00:09:34,330 --> 00:09:36,200
<Default><b>If I choose
to believe her</b></Default>

150
00:09:36,909 --> 00:09:38,949
<Default><b>will that put everyone
in danger?</b></Default>

151
00:09:40,909 --> 00:09:42,330
<Default><b>Master Naofumi.</b></Default>

152
00:09:43,210 --> 00:09:45,840
<Default><b>She stepped in and saved
our lives back there.</b></Default>

153
00:09:46,340 --> 00:09:47,816
<Default><b>What's the worst that
could happen</b></Default>

154
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:50,120
<Default><b>if we let her stay with us
for a while?</b></Default>

155
00:09:51,590 --> 00:09:52,759
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

156
00:09:53,720 --> 00:09:55,576
<Default><b>I don't fully
trust her yet.</b></Default>

157
00:09:55,600 --> 00:09:57,440
<Default><b>So I'll keep
an eye on her.</b></Default>

158
00:09:57,519 --> 00:09:58,850
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

159
00:10:11,529 --> 00:10:13,089
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

160
00:10:23,460 --> 00:10:25,020
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

161
00:10:26,840 --> 00:10:29,040
<Default><b>[kid 1] Make it sit
on my hand, miss!</b></Default>

162
00:10:29,710 --> 00:10:31,310
<Default><b>[kid 2] On mine, too!</b></Default>

163
00:10:31,879 --> 00:10:33,905
<Default><b>She's made a lot
of friends already, huh?</b></Default>

164
00:10:33,929 --> 00:10:35,129
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

165
00:10:36,090 --> 00:10:38,009
<Default><b>[KEEL]
Hey, Naofumi!</b></Default>

166
00:10:38,100 --> 00:10:39,100
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

167
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:41,850
<Default><b>We're finally back
from training!</b></Default>

168
00:10:42,019 --> 00:10:44,440
<Default><b>Good. I'm guessing
it went well, then?</b></Default>

169
00:10:44,940 --> 00:10:46,125
<Default><b>There was
certainly a lot</b></Default>

170
00:10:46,149 --> 00:10:47,956
<Default><b>they were able to learn
from the training.</b></Default>

171
00:10:47,980 --> 00:10:49,769
<Default><b>So next</b></Default>

172
00:10:49,860 --> 00:10:52,149
<Default><b>actual combat
alongside Rishia.</b></Default>

173
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:53,625
<Default><b>I'm sure that
there's a lot more</b></Default>

174
00:10:53,649 --> 00:10:54,755
<Default><b>training to be done.</b></Default>

175
00:10:54,779 --> 00:10:57,659
<Default><b>What we've learned is only
the surface of Hengen Muso.</b></Default>

176
00:10:59,659 --> 00:11:02,620
<Default><b>You see, anybody's capable
of learning that much.</b></Default>

177
00:11:02,870 --> 00:11:05,395
<Default><b>But only promising students
can learn the secrets</b></Default>

178
00:11:05,419 --> 00:11:07,019
<Default><b>that lie beyond that.</b></Default>

179
00:11:08,750 --> 00:11:09,919
<Default><b>And?</b></Default>

180
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:12,105
<Default><b>What about your duty
to run these lands?</b></Default>

181
00:11:12,129 --> 00:11:14,329
<Default><b>Have you put Melty
in charge of that?</b></Default>

182
00:11:15,879 --> 00:11:18,259
<Default><b>Oh, we have
a new visitor in the village.</b></Default>

183
00:11:18,970 --> 00:11:20,865
<Default><b>But we don't know
if they're friend or foe.</b></Default>

184
00:11:20,889 --> 00:11:22,696
<Default><b>[DEMI-HUMAN GIRL 05-C]
One more time!</b></Default>

185
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:25,600
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] It's dangerous
to not have you here, Eclair.</b></Default>

186
00:11:26,019 --> 00:11:27,100
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

187
00:11:27,559 --> 00:11:29,719
<Default><b>I know
it's important to be training</b></Default>

188
00:11:29,809 --> 00:11:31,586
<Default><b>but you should try to think
about our lands</b></Default>

189
00:11:31,610 --> 00:11:33,125
<Default><b>and our business, too.</b></Default>

190
00:11:33,149 --> 00:11:34,649
<Default><b>Ah, all right.</b></Default>

191
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:37,046
<Default><b>And hey, Naofumi,
guess what?</b></Default>

192
00:11:37,070 --> 00:11:39,159
<Default><b>What?
Something happen, Keel?</b></Default>

193
00:11:39,950 --> 00:11:40,870
<Default><b>We trained so much</b></Default>

194
00:11:40,950 --> 00:11:42,990
<Default><b>our levels went up
a whole bunch!</b></Default>

195
00:11:49,340 --> 00:11:50,789
<Default><b>[laughing]</b></Default>

196
00:11:53,049 --> 00:11:54,849
<Default><b>See for yourself,
Naofumi!</b></Default>

197
00:11:56,090 --> 00:11:57,299
<Default><b>Sure.</b></Default>

198
00:12:04,970 --> 00:12:07,850
<Default><b>Impressive, you could
upgrade your classes now.</b></Default>

199
00:12:07,940 --> 00:12:09,899
<Default><b>Upgrade our classes!</b></Default>

200
00:12:11,269 --> 00:12:14,399
<Default><b>- Hey, Filo!
- Yes?</b></Default>

201
00:12:14,490 --> 00:12:16,950
<Default><b>Anything I can do
for you, Master?</b></Default>

202
00:12:19,779 --> 00:12:21,979
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
We're doing class upgrades.</b></Default>

203
00:12:22,450 --> 00:12:24,909
<Default><b>But what about
the Spear guy.</b></Default>

204
00:12:27,039 --> 00:12:28,419
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

205
00:12:31,830 --> 00:12:33,129
<Default><b>Filo!</b></Default>

206
00:12:35,960 --> 00:12:38,049
<Default><b>[MOTOYASU] Filo!</b></Default>

207
00:12:42,100 --> 00:12:44,785
<Default><b>If we see him, you can just
give him a good, hard kick</b></Default>

208
00:12:44,809 --> 00:12:46,035
<Default><b>like you usually do.</b></Default>

209
00:12:46,059 --> 00:12:47,619
<Default><b>But, Master Naofumi.</b></Default>

210
00:12:47,769 --> 00:12:50,559
<Default><b>If you're like Keel</b></Default>

211
00:12:50,649 --> 00:12:52,009
<Default><b>then follow me.</b></Default>

212
00:12:52,559 --> 00:12:55,639
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] We're going to the
capital right after breakfast.</b></Default>

213
00:13:01,450 --> 00:13:04,255
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Upgrading your class
expands your potential</b></Default>

214
00:13:04,279 --> 00:13:05,926
<Default><b>but also
risks limiting it</b></Default>

215
00:13:05,950 --> 00:13:08,370
<Default><b>but the benefits it brings
are worthwhile.</b></Default>

216
00:13:08,870 --> 00:13:10,556
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] It's entirely
possible that something</b></Default>

217
00:13:10,580 --> 00:13:12,860
<Default><b>unexpected could
happen to you as well.</b></Default>

218
00:13:13,789 --> 00:13:15,750
<Default><b>You may not be
able to choose.</b></Default>

219
00:13:15,840 --> 00:13:17,186
<Default><b>You could get
assigned a class</b></Default>

220
00:13:17,210 --> 00:13:19,485
<Default><b>where you have the most
potential for growth</b></Default>

221
00:13:19,509 --> 00:13:21,669
<Default><b>even if you're
not proficient in it.</b></Default>

222
00:13:22,179 --> 00:13:25,429
<Default><b>That said, in the lives
you still have ahead of you</b></Default>

223
00:13:25,809 --> 00:13:28,600
<Default><b>fighting ability isn't
the only thing that matters.</b></Default>

224
00:13:29,100 --> 00:13:31,309
<Default><b>Imiya is good
with her hands, right?</b></Default>

225
00:13:31,690 --> 00:13:33,899
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] And Ushiko</b></Default>

226
00:13:34,269 --> 00:13:35,796
<Default><b>If there's something
you want to do</b></Default>

227
00:13:35,820 --> 00:13:38,086
<Default><b>choosing to specialize
in that specific talent</b></Default>

228
00:13:38,110 --> 00:13:40,390
<Default><b>will have a huge impact
on your future.</b></Default>

229
00:13:40,529 --> 00:13:42,426
<Default><b>So make a choice
you won't regret.</b></Default>

230
00:13:42,450 --> 00:13:43,490
<Default><b>[grunt]</b></Default>

231
00:13:44,120 --> 00:13:45,200
<Default><b>Easy!</b></Default>

232
00:13:45,370 --> 00:13:47,130
<Default><b>I just wanna
be stronger!</b></Default>

233
00:13:48,370 --> 00:13:50,850
<Default><b>[KEEL] I'll do whatever
it takes to do that!</b></Default>

234
00:13:52,169 --> 00:13:54,919
<Default><b>- So I don't need to choose!
- What he said!</b></Default>

235
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:56,855
<Default><b>I want to choose
to be strong, too!</b></Default>

236
00:13:56,879 --> 00:14:00,009
<Default><b>I already made up my mind
and decided to be a chef!</b></Default>

237
00:14:00,090 --> 00:14:03,220
<Default><b>Good. Now the rest of you.
Split into two groups.</b></Default>

238
00:14:03,590 --> 00:14:06,100
<Default><b>Those who want to choose</b></Default>

239
00:14:06,259 --> 00:14:07,720
<Default><b>[ALL] Okay!</b></Default>

240
00:14:24,409 --> 00:14:27,990
<Default><b>[KEEL] [laughing]
I want this one! No this one.</b></Default>

241
00:14:28,330 --> 00:14:30,659
<Default><b>They're all so amazing</b></Default>

242
00:14:31,080 --> 00:14:32,476
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Is your work on new shields</b></Default>

243
00:14:32,500 --> 00:14:34,140
<Default><b>and armor progressing?</b></Default>

244
00:14:34,289 --> 00:14:35,960
<Default><b>Not even a little bit!</b></Default>

245
00:14:36,169 --> 00:14:38,609
<Default><b>I've got a bunch
of prototypes, although...</b></Default>

246
00:14:40,460 --> 00:14:41,960
<Default><b>It's so heavy!</b></Default>

247
00:14:42,509 --> 00:14:44,566
<Default><b>The ore you brought
from the Spirit Tortoise</b></Default>

248
00:14:44,590 --> 00:14:46,929
<Default><b>is a little weird
to say the least.</b></Default>

249
00:14:47,139 --> 00:14:49,099
<Default><b>It makes it hard
to work with.</b></Default>

250
00:14:49,179 --> 00:14:50,196
<Default><b>[ELHART]
This one's light</b></Default>

251
00:14:50,220 --> 00:14:52,340
<Default><b>but it'll break
in a single strike.</b></Default>

252
00:14:53,730 --> 00:14:55,600
<Default><b>So, it's
basically a plate?</b></Default>

253
00:14:55,690 --> 00:14:58,149
<Default><b>Yeah, I'm sure
I'll find a balance though.</b></Default>

254
00:14:58,480 --> 00:15:00,230
<Default><b>So, what is it you need?</b></Default>

255
00:15:00,320 --> 00:15:03,649
<Default><b>Oh, you see, we just
upgraded our classes.</b></Default>

256
00:15:03,740 --> 00:15:06,460
<Default><b>And so I figured, since
we're getting new weapons.</b></Default>

257
00:15:07,830 --> 00:15:10,426
<Default><b>I'd bring a slave from
the village to talk to you.</b></Default>

258
00:15:10,450 --> 00:15:11,909
<Default><b>Why a slave?</b></Default>

259
00:15:11,990 --> 00:15:13,710
<Default><b>- Go on, Keel.
- Right!</b></Default>

260
00:15:15,409 --> 00:15:18,289
<Default><b>Believe it or not he said
he wants to be a blacksmith.</b></Default>

261
00:15:18,460 --> 00:15:20,060
<Default><b>[KEEL]
Hey, come here!</b></Default>

262
00:15:21,509 --> 00:15:24,429
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Think you could
take him on as an apprentice?</b></Default>

263
00:15:24,509 --> 00:15:25,549
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

264
00:15:27,009 --> 00:15:28,340
<Default><b>Tollynemiya!</b></Default>

265
00:15:30,759 --> 00:15:32,559
<Default><b>It's good to
see you again</b></Default>

266
00:15:32,769 --> 00:15:34,289
<Default><b>Wait, you know him?</b></Default>

267
00:15:34,389 --> 00:15:35,405
<Default><b>[TOLLYNEMIYA]
Yeah</b></Default>

268
00:15:35,429 --> 00:15:37,549
<Default><b>we actually
used to train together.</b></Default>

269
00:15:37,940 --> 00:15:40,540
<Default><b>Although, I never would've
imagined I'd be here</b></Default>

270
00:15:40,570 --> 00:15:42,206
<Default><b>learning to be
a blacksmith from you!</b></Default>

271
00:15:42,230 --> 00:15:44,270
<Default><b>I'm just as surprised
as you are!</b></Default>

272
00:15:45,240 --> 00:15:46,760
<Default><b>[KEEL]
Hey, Naofumi!</b></Default>

273
00:15:47,029 --> 00:15:49,830
<Default><b>Once we get
our new weapons</b></Default>

274
00:15:49,909 --> 00:15:52,265
<Default><b>I'm itching to get
into a fight right now!</b></Default>

275
00:15:52,289 --> 00:15:54,080
<Default><b>Bring it on</b></Default>

276
00:15:54,159 --> 00:15:55,450
<Default><b>[chuckle]</b></Default>

277
00:15:59,629 --> 00:16:02,000
<Default><b>Hunting! Hunting!</b></Default>

278
00:16:02,090 --> 00:16:03,530
<Default><b>Time for hunting!</b></Default>

279
00:16:07,340 --> 00:16:08,929
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

280
00:16:11,259 --> 00:16:12,785
<Default><b>C'mon, one more time!</b></Default>

281
00:16:12,809 --> 00:16:15,519
<Default><b>We'll practice it
as many times as you like.</b></Default>

282
00:16:15,600 --> 00:16:17,059
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

283
00:16:18,850 --> 00:16:20,916
<Default><b>His movements
are getting sharper.</b></Default>

284
00:16:20,940 --> 00:16:22,320
<Default><b>Yes.</b></Default>

285
00:16:22,399 --> 00:16:23,570
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

286
00:16:27,450 --> 00:16:29,546
<Default><b>You've still got
a lot to learn, kid.</b></Default>

287
00:16:29,570 --> 00:16:32,135
<Default><b>What was that technique
you used on him just now?</b></Default>

288
00:16:32,159 --> 00:16:33,765
<Default><b>That move is
one of the various</b></Default>

289
00:16:33,789 --> 00:16:35,909
<Default><b>secret techniques
of Hengen Muso.</b></Default>

290
00:16:36,080 --> 00:16:37,726
<Default><b>And it looks like
Atla's walking around</b></Default>

291
00:16:37,750 --> 00:16:39,789
<Default><b>- a lot more than before.
- Yes.</b></Default>

292
00:16:40,210 --> 00:16:41,810
<Default><b>[ATLA]
Mister Naofumi!</b></Default>

293
00:16:41,840 --> 00:16:42,840
<Default><b>Yeah?</b></Default>

294
00:16:42,879 --> 00:16:44,359
<Default><b>Come look at this!</b></Default>

295
00:16:45,049 --> 00:16:46,929
<Default><b>Can you help
me out, Rishia?</b></Default>

296
00:16:47,220 --> 00:16:48,419
<Default><b>Sure!</b></Default>

297
00:16:51,179 --> 00:16:52,739
<Default><b>Go ahead, I'm ready.</b></Default>

298
00:16:52,929 --> 00:16:54,209
<Default><b>Here it goes!</b></Default>

299
00:17:03,190 --> 00:17:05,359
<Default><b>She's improving
so quickly.</b></Default>

300
00:17:06,279 --> 00:17:07,559
<Default><b>You're right.</b></Default>

301
00:17:08,740 --> 00:17:10,660
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Atla, You got a sec?</b></Default>

302
00:17:11,279 --> 00:17:13,700
<Default><b>- Yes.
- We're taking you hunting.</b></Default>

303
00:17:14,119 --> 00:17:15,029
<Default><b>Yay!</b></Default>

304
00:17:15,119 --> 00:17:17,386
<Default><b>I've been looking forward
to hunting with you!</b></Default>

305
00:17:17,410 --> 00:17:19,450
<Default><b>Thank you
for including me in it.</b></Default>

306
00:17:20,119 --> 00:17:21,599
<Default><b>Let me go instead!</b></Default>

307
00:17:21,920 --> 00:17:24,420
<Default><b>It's not safe for you
to go hunting, Atla.</b></Default>

308
00:17:24,670 --> 00:17:27,839
<Default><b>You worry too much.
I'll be fine, brother!</b></Default>

309
00:17:35,970 --> 00:17:37,390
<Default><b>[laughing]</b></Default>

310
00:17:38,730 --> 00:17:41,370
<Default><b>What's with that really
weird sound you let out?</b></Default>

311
00:17:42,599 --> 00:17:45,690
<Default><b>If you keep
laughing like that</b></Default>

312
00:17:46,230 --> 00:17:48,279
<Default><b>I can laugh all I want to!
Hmph!</b></Default>

313
00:17:49,319 --> 00:17:52,200
<Default><b>- You can come too, Fohl.
- A-All right!</b></Default>

314
00:17:52,740 --> 00:17:54,700
<Default><b>Just stick with
me okay, Atla?</b></Default>

315
00:17:55,240 --> 00:17:58,289
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Now, Atla and Fohl
can come along with us.</b></Default>

316
00:17:58,910 --> 00:18:01,210
<Default><b>We've got you</b></Default>

317
00:18:01,289 --> 00:18:03,710
<Default><b>And Filo so we can
get around faster.</b></Default>

318
00:18:03,880 --> 00:18:05,289
<Default><b>Raphy.</b></Default>

319
00:18:06,130 --> 00:18:07,896
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
You want to come too, Raphy?</b></Default>

320
00:18:07,920 --> 00:18:09,339
<Default><b>Raphy.</b></Default>

321
00:18:11,930 --> 00:18:14,330
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] The question is
what do we hunt?</b></Default>

322
00:18:14,759 --> 00:18:17,640
<Default><b>If I may, Naofumi</b></Default>

323
00:18:18,220 --> 00:18:20,446
<Default><b>After the situation
that occurred with the slavers</b></Default>

324
00:18:20,470 --> 00:18:21,309
<Default><b>the other day</b></Default>

325
00:18:21,390 --> 00:18:23,910
<Default><b>I went and took a good look
around our lands.</b></Default>

326
00:18:24,599 --> 00:18:26,495
<Default><b>[ECLAIR] During the
Spirit Tortoise's march</b></Default>

327
00:18:26,519 --> 00:18:28,835
<Default><b>it destroyed a facility
that our nation managed</b></Default>

328
00:18:28,859 --> 00:18:30,359
<Default><b>as a penal colony.</b></Default>

329
00:18:30,650 --> 00:18:33,240
<Default><b>Most of the prisoners there
died, however...</b></Default>

330
00:18:33,819 --> 00:18:36,779
<Default><b>[ECLAIR] It seems there were
also a number of survivors.</b></Default>

331
00:18:37,869 --> 00:18:40,549
<Default><b>Many of them were part
of the Three Heroes Church</b></Default>

332
00:18:40,579 --> 00:18:42,936
<Default><b>who'd been sent there
after what happened to you.</b></Default>

333
00:18:42,960 --> 00:18:45,555
<Default><b>And those were the same slavers
who attacked the village</b></Default>

334
00:18:45,579 --> 00:18:46,899
<Default><b>after we left?</b></Default>

335
00:18:48,750 --> 00:18:50,815
<Default><b>There's no way of knowing
if the two incidents</b></Default>

336
00:18:50,839 --> 00:18:52,025
<Default><b>are related.</b></Default>

337
00:18:52,049 --> 00:18:55,299
<Default><b>While the church
is a concern</b></Default>

338
00:18:55,380 --> 00:18:58,220
<Default><b>about criminals who may
have fled the Spirit Tortoise</b></Default>

339
00:18:58,349 --> 00:19:00,509
<Default><b>so I went and patrolled
our lands.</b></Default>

340
00:19:01,890 --> 00:19:03,666
<Default><b>[ECLAIR] It was then
that I heard about a group</b></Default>

341
00:19:03,690 --> 00:19:06,349
<Default><b>of bandits that has been
active as of late.</b></Default>

342
00:19:07,359 --> 00:19:08,759
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] I see.</b></Default>

343
00:19:10,230 --> 00:19:12,710
<Default><b>So we can test our strength
by hunting them.</b></Default>

344
00:19:13,240 --> 00:19:15,240
<Default><b>Do you want to
come along, too?</b></Default>

345
00:19:15,279 --> 00:19:16,439
<Default><b>Of course.</b></Default>

346
00:19:17,119 --> 00:19:19,595
<Default><b>[ECLAIR] Their leader
is supposedly a tough opponent</b></Default>

347
00:19:19,619 --> 00:19:22,079
<Default><b>who's known
for not making any mistakes.</b></Default>

348
00:19:22,750 --> 00:19:24,550
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
What do you mean?</b></Default>

349
00:19:24,710 --> 00:19:27,015
<Default><b>[ECLAIR]
He's an extremely cautious man.</b></Default>

350
00:19:27,039 --> 00:19:30,210
<Default><b>He's sneaky and never
lets his band be seen.</b></Default>

351
00:19:30,339 --> 00:19:32,686
<Default><b>They only attack people
who've gotten separated</b></Default>

352
00:19:32,710 --> 00:19:34,270
<Default><b>from their comrades.</b></Default>

353
00:19:34,759 --> 00:19:37,479
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Which means
he'll be tough to deal with.</b></Default>

354
00:19:40,180 --> 00:19:42,325
<Default><b>Our best bet is to split up
into groups</b></Default>

355
00:19:42,349 --> 00:19:44,285
<Default><b>and search
for the bandits' hideout.</b></Default>

356
00:19:44,309 --> 00:19:45,709
<Default><b>Filo and Rishia.</b></Default>

357
00:19:46,599 --> 00:19:49,190
<Default><b>- Eclair, Fohl, and Atla.
- Sure.</b></Default>

358
00:19:50,980 --> 00:19:52,545
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Raphtalia and Keel.</b></Default>

359
00:19:52,569 --> 00:19:54,249
<Default><b>Who are you going with?</b></Default>

360
00:19:54,319 --> 00:19:56,626
<Default><b>I'll be teaming up
with Raphy, of course.</b></Default>

361
00:19:56,650 --> 00:19:58,319
<Default><b>Raphy.</b></Default>

362
00:20:09,289 --> 00:20:11,799
<Default><b>Those white tiger
children from before.</b></Default>

363
00:20:16,970 --> 00:20:19,849
<Default><b>The younger sister's
name was Atla, correct?</b></Default>

364
00:20:20,509 --> 00:20:23,029
<Default><b>[AULTCRAY] She was
the spitting image of her.</b></Default>

365
00:20:23,349 --> 00:20:24,669
<Default><b>[MIRELIA] Yes.</b></Default>

366
00:20:27,059 --> 00:20:29,206
<Default><b>[ATLA] I was really hoping
to fight alongside</b></Default>

367
00:20:29,230 --> 00:20:30,590
<Default><b>Mister Naofumi.</b></Default>

368
00:20:30,809 --> 00:20:33,416
<Default><b>[FOHL] You're safer staying
behind me and watching!</b></Default>

369
00:20:33,440 --> 00:20:35,720
<Default><b>[ECLAIR]
Try and stay focused, you two.</b></Default>

370
00:20:36,609 --> 00:20:39,169
<Default><b>[FILO] I wonder if there's
any food over here.</b></Default>

371
00:20:39,240 --> 00:20:40,466
<Default><b>[RISHIA]
Come on, Filo!</b></Default>

372
00:20:40,490 --> 00:20:43,369
<Default><b>We're supposed to be looking
for bandits, not food!</b></Default>

373
00:20:44,079 --> 00:20:45,386
<Default><b>[KEEL]
Where are those bandits hiding?</b></Default>

374
00:20:45,410 --> 00:20:46,890
<Default><b>I'm ready for 'em!</b></Default>

375
00:20:47,000 --> 00:20:50,080
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA] This isn't the time
to be messing around, Keel.</b></Default>

376
00:20:51,960 --> 00:20:53,646
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Eclair said
the bandits' leader</b></Default>

377
00:20:53,670 --> 00:20:55,950
<Default><b>attacks people
who are traveling alone.</b></Default>

378
00:20:56,799 --> 00:21:00,630
<Default><b>So to take
advantage of that</b></Default>

379
00:21:01,720 --> 00:21:03,406
<Default><b>If the bandits set up
an ambush</b></Default>

380
00:21:03,430 --> 00:21:05,430
<Default><b>then I can handle it
no problem.</b></Default>

381
00:21:05,470 --> 00:21:06,745
<Default><b>Right, Raphy?</b></Default>

382
00:21:06,769 --> 00:21:08,349
<Default><b>Raphy!</b></Default>

383
00:21:09,390 --> 00:21:11,309
<Default><b>Raphy, Raphy, Ra...</b></Default>

384
00:21:12,059 --> 00:21:14,099
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
What? Is someone there?</b></Default>

385
00:21:20,240 --> 00:21:21,819
<Default><b>Raphy. Raphy.</b></Default>

386
00:21:32,710 --> 00:21:34,250
<Default><b>Motoyasu?</b></Default>

387
00:21:35,049 --> 00:21:36,670
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

388
00:21:45,549 --> 00:21:46,809
<Default><b>Ren?</b></Default>

389
00:21:46,890 --> 00:21:49,349
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

